# Malay Pantun Classification System — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A full-stack **Malay Pantun Theme Classification System** using SVM that classifies pantun into 11 themes. The system follows the methodology from the research paper (Chapter 3).

### Architecture
```
frontend/ (Next.js + TypeScript)  →  backend/ (Flask + SVM)
   Port 3000                           Port 5000
```

---

## Data Cleaning

Processed **7 raw Excel files** (7,376 pantun) with 108 different theme names, mapped to **11 standardized themes**, merged with existing [pantun_cleaned_v2.json](file:///c:/Users/rahim/pantun-classification-enchanced/pantun_cleaned_v2.json), and deduplicated.

**Final dataset**: [pantun_dataset.json](file:///c:/Users/rahim/pantun-classification-enchanced/pantun_dataset.json) — **9,124 pantun**

| Theme | Count |
|---|---|
| PANTUN NASIHAT DAN PENDIDIKAN | 1,987 |
| PANTUN PERIBAHASA DAN PERBILANGAN | 1,692 |
| PANTUN KIAS DAN IBARAT | 1,261 |
| PANTUN PERCINTAAN | 1,155 |
| PANTUN ADAT DAN RESAM | 999 |
| PANTUN JENAKA DAN PERMAINAN | 525 |
| PANTUN BUDI | 413 |
| PANTUN AGAMA DAN KEPERCAYAAN | 358 |
| PANTUN KEPAHLAWANAN | 342 |
| PANTUN KEMBARA DAN PERANTAUAN | 252 |
| PANTUN TEKA-TEKI | 141 |

---

## SVM Model Training

Trained **6 models** (3 data splits × 2 pembayang settings):

| Model | Accuracy | F1-Score |
|---|---|---|
| svm_90-10_no_pembayang ⭐ | 55.1% | 0.533 |
| svm_80-20_no_pembayang | 53.0% | 0.516 |
| svm_90-10_pembayang | 52.5% | 0.513 |
| svm_80-20_pembayang | 50.6% | 0.493 |
| svm_70-30_no_pembayang | 51.9% | 0.501 |
| svm_70-30_pembayang | 49.6% | 0.479 |

> [!NOTE]
> Without pembayang consistently outperforms with pembayang, validating the Chapter 3 methodology that theme meaning resides in the maksud (lines 3-4). TextCNN and MalayBERT (via Google Colab) are expected to significantly improve these scores.

