<!-- slide -->
![Classification result — PANTUN ADAT DAN RESAM at 98.6% confidence](/C:/Users/rahim/.gemini/antigravity/brain/7c143f3c-efc8-4475-8429-db5615bdba22/final_result_verification_1772663532287.png)
